plugin: manual
id: gnome-clocks
flags: simple
_description:
 PURPOSE:
       Check that gnome-clocks runs and works correctly
 STEPS:
      1. Run gnome-clocks from the desktop icon. Does the icon look correct?
      2. Make sure hamburger menu -> Help brings up the Help page
      3. Add two different world clocks and verify the time difference is correct
      4. Set an alarm and make sure it beeps at you when it goes off
      5. Start and stop the stopwatch
      6. Set a timer and make sure it dings at you when it goes off

unit: test plan
id: gnome-clocks-tp
name: gnome-clocks test plan
include: gnome-clocks
